When my mother passed away it was I had to create a go fund me for my mother because she didn’t have any life insurance, and I appreciate all the help but honestly it was hard!!!!! Especially asking for help and hoping we reached the goal, plus grieving and stressing with no funds to put my queen to rest, but I thank GOD for all my beautiful supporters who helped me 🙏🏼😞 Life insurance is so important!!! Seriously! It’s only $25 a month! This is a must have! this is something we don’t talk about but this is serious!!!!!!! we weren’t raised up on how important life insurance is. When we decided to get life insurance for my mother, they told us NO! Because she already has been diagnosed with cancer so they declined us. After my mother passed away I said “I’m signing myself up for some life insurance it’s important!” It can be very stressful trying to find money while you’re grieving. Life insurance not only helps you pay for funerals, but gives money to your family ❤️ SIGN YOURSELF YOUR CHILD UP PLEASE 🙏🏼

Look how my face slim down in a year! 

A lot of people who don’t know me say I lost a lot of weight. No I didn’t loose weight I went back to my normal size I was never Big. I started gaining weight after my mother past away and didn’t noticed how much I was over eating bad processed food. And junk food. 

When I went to my doctor she told me I need to loose weight and change my diet because I was a board line diabetic and board line from having heart disease from eating unhealthy fried food and junk food 24/7

Well it’s been a full since i didn’t have  a soda I don’t eat junk food I don’t eat fast food I don’t eat bread I don’t drink juice! I don’t eat nothing bad to harm my body 

I changed my eating habits and drink a lot water and plenty of fruits and I actually bake my food. 

changing my eating habits was HARD I’m not going lie this was one of the hardest life changing things I ever went through. it’s a mental thing. But now you can’t pay me to eat fast food or drink juice or a soda or eat candy! I had to make a decision do I want to be a diabetic. I’m now more energized ❤️ and more healthy now. I love it 🥰 

Go healthy if you want to live long 

Health is wealth 

I’m proud of myself ❤️
